{"tid":455292,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打知點解用水煲意粉要落鹽？","createTime":"2017-11-02T03:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T04:24:01.000Z","uid":123335,"like":7,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"50690e42b7506698ef358d472b983f4382d2dee9","tid":455292,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:00:25.000Z","msg":"上網google 左話係想增加水入面既離子，<br />\n令到用水煲果時會更有穿透性<br />\n<br />\n聽完都唔知係唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我又有諗過因為d意粉係外國進口，<br />\n落鹽係for 外國d 硬水，<br />\n落d 鹽好似會中和返d 硬水會軟水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌<br />\n其實我都係唔知點解煮意粉要落鹽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e7ee95cd260d6f24e8759fa7f9c1459802ac77","tid":455292,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:00:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上網google 左話係想增加水入面既離子，<br />\n令到用水煲果時會更有穿透性<br />\n<br />\n聽完都唔知係唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我又有諗過因為d意粉係外國進口，<br />\n落鹽係for 外國d 硬水，<br />\n落d 鹽好似會中和返d 硬水<span style=\"color: red;\">變</span>軟水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌<br />\n其實我都係唔知點解煮意粉要落鹽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a2475914e2ccfbe673b805bdad4b300d9b5d53ae","tid":455292,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:02:07.000Z","msg":"有冇煮食達人help me"},{"pid":"5ef023ea1039befc713532069dc6a7a9b06cf77a","tid":455292,"uid":31752,"like":53,"dislike":5,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:09:39.000Z","msg":"直接用鹽水煮咪唔洗再調味囉"},{"pid":"2c0d1c15a2d730c05112c292efa9f7ed1e8862d9","tid":455292,"uid":70183,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:10:09.000Z","msg":"沸點唔同左"},{"pid":"08265618823802c74cd6c06a1edd8101c0571f2c","tid":455292,"uid":45431,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:10:58.000Z","msg":"等啲水可以再熱啲"},{"pid":"4ca46719dc9fe4cfecbf53052a7dc945af2