"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:18:01.000Z","msg":"減低滲透作用 <br />\n等條意粉煮完會彈牙啲"},{"pid":"2915ffc722abbed7e1b562109e4dace51bfc687d","tid":455292,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:18:33.000Z","msg":"唔係要落油咩"},{"pid":"8f792c76caf823a5703b9a64f80e942d70178c39","tid":455292,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:19:00.000Z","msg":"有味d囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ab30b600d88b8d3bd847f632f8ced03c1ff61d","tid":455292,"uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:21:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>沸點唔同左</blockquote><br />\n高左？</blockquote><br />\n低左<br />\n<br />\n另外，我估可能係<br />\n密度高左，令意粉味冇咁易流失<br />\n<br />\n加埋密度高左啲粉易浮啲，更易做到轉轉轉個效果<br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩吹，可能只係為左令啲粉有味</blockquote><br />\n沸點低左姐係, <br />\n姐係原本D水100度就滾<br />\n落左鹽, D水90度就滾<br />\n<br />\n會唔會係D意粉用低溫D, e.g. 90度, 去煮會好食D ?"},{"pid":"191a013dea0865e455eab85623994a2c0970a104","tid":455292,"uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:22:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">減低滲透作用</span> <br />\n等條意粉煮完會彈牙啲</blockquote><br />\n大師, 呢話何解 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bacb3cd6626f81449666092607e449ef1049b9","tid":455292,"uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:23:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有味d囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點解我唔落糖 ?"},{"pid":"0b230d6790793d8aa96728b1e3a5ed893b8fe965","tid":455292,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:23:31.000Z","msg":"俾啲味佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 意粉磁通量"},{"pid":"62c451860329ed89cc17598f8d8ade7c60975eb9","tid":455292,"uid":137912,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:23:43.000Z","msg":"Gordon Ramsay : seasoning"},{"pid":"da1563277e60e10e2c4b2ea6561a8b73322aadcc","tid":455292,"uid":45431,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:23:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>沸點唔同左</blockquote><br />\n高左？</blockquote><br />\n低左<br />\n<br />\n另外，我估可能係<br />\n密度高左，令意粉味冇咁易流失<br />\n<br />\n加埋密度高左啲粉易浮啲，更易做到轉轉轉個效果<br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩吹，可能只係為左令啲粉有味</blockquote><br />\n沸點低左姐係, <br />\n姐係原本D水100度就滾<br />\n落左鹽, D水90度就滾<br />\n<br />\n會唔會係D意粉用低溫D, e.g. 90度, 去煮會好食D ?</blockquote><br />\n高左呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落左鹽可以上到10x度，水熱啲煮出黎好食啲"},{"pid":"cf5f70cfb19a4c57357d98b6f82dfa8167b57102","tid":455292,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:24:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有味d囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點解我唔落糖 ?</blockquote><br />\n你可以試下睇下咩味 <br />\n留名"},{"pid":"2febafc3f2734ebce365cfd827abca4d9609d100","tid":455292,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:25:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係要落油咩</blockquote><br />\n各施各法<br />\n但新鮮意粉要落，如果唔係未硬嗰時會有機會痴埋一舊"},{"pid":"e0d87e32823c7b171dc64f9f77692f49cfed638f","tid":455292,"uid":27596,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:25:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>沸點唔同左</blockquote><br />\n高左？</blockquote><br />\n低左<br />\n<br />\n另外，我估可能係<br />\n密度高左，令意粉味冇咁易流失<br />\n<br />\n加埋密度高左啲粉易浮啲，更易做到轉轉轉個效果<br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩吹，可能只係為左令啲粉有味</blockquote><br />\n純粹為咗意粉有少少味，會吊到汁個味出啲"},{"pid":"3aa7a8f6b2a8930bde980b2f0c06390cb564b090","tid":455292,"uid":43570,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:25:53.000Z","msg":"真係純粹調味....<br />\n<br />\n咁多水，咁少鹽，升得果兩三度，又點會有分別...分分鐘水裏面個溫差都超過呢個數..."},{"pid":"c5193bd5fba4e1988197cad4f4af759316fcc31e","tid":455292,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:26:33.000Z","msg":"冇咁易痴住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88656fdc5bf471b7a8d7a90c205542545d7d4bf","tid":455292,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有味d囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點解我唔落糖 ?</blockquote><br />\n你可以試下睇下咩味 <br />\n留名</blockquote><br />\n有味啲唔係正確解釋，一來真係落少少鹽，唔至於令到意粉鹹味。<br />\n二來當你落好多落到意粉有鹹味，你最後煮醬呀調味呀會好困難。"},{"pid":"bcdfbbb89c2ffeb8f35f643e95f3e34eb90ae128","tid":455292,"uid":66870,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:28:07.000Z","msg":"Up mud 9?"},{"pid":"d18af4c4c9fef50685bae95e35232b5aa02358c5","tid":455292,"uid":36359,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:28:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有味d囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點解我唔落糖 ?</blockquote><br />\n你想碟意粉係甜既咪落囉 <br />\n點解落鹽唔落糖都問得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c001a54e98d5e2e197794e42a371465949c6a653","tid":455292,"uid":45431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:29:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係純粹調味....<br />\n<br />\n咁多水，咁少鹽，升得果兩三度，又點會有分別...分分鐘水裏面個溫差都超過呢個數...</blockquote><br />\n你都識講咁少鹽，點調味?<br />\n差幾度就係差幾度，你試下去高原，水只能去到九十度左右，啲麵一係生，一係熟到爛。"},{"pid":"a2bf9e3326016731ed56d6b5bcad9da600a356ee","tid":455292,"uid":43570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:30:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇咁易痴住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個同水溫有關，當意粉d starch溶左落水，但溫度未升起，佢會好黏，所以煮意粉一開始時先要搞下啲粉。當水溫上升，starch被改變構造就唔會再黏，所以就唔洗再搞。<br />\n<br />\n因為成日煮意粉所以睇過下個化學作用...."},{"pid":"c30b7643a51c31c6385691791632fa0f1447dbd1","tid":455292,"uid":1558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:30:54.000Z","msg":"我自己試過，落左最大既分別係在於你其後有汁果陣啲味會融合啲"},{"pid":"567b8cf996835b93357b55c8729695846dd7e007","tid":455292,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:31:15.000Z","msg":"應該係會有味, 唔落就好淡"},{"pid":"bbbaf06a454edacc9c9614af7043dbd7ab97b42a","tid":455292,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:31:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>沸點唔同左</blockquote><br />\n高左？</blockquote><br />\n低左<br />\n<br />\n另外，我估可能係<br />\n密度高左，令意粉味冇咁易流失<br />\n<br />\n加埋密度高左啲粉易浮啲，更易做到轉轉轉個效果<br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩吹，可能只係為左令啲粉有味</blockquote><br />\n沸點低左姐係, <br />\n姐係原本D水100度就滾<br />\n落左鹽, D水90度就滾<br />\n<br />\n會唔會係D意粉用低溫D, e.g. 90度, 去煮會好食D ?</blockquote><br />\n高左呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落左鹽可以上到10x度，水熱啲煮出黎好食啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsorry,自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b6cc53091920cd4af430adae94196c922979e8","tid":455292,"uid":23592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:31:17.000Z","msg":"調味"},{"pid":"5b7cb1c72d6539138c419bfeea0d9d18830d7c83","tid":455292,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:33:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真係純粹調味....<br />\n<br />\n咁多水，咁少鹽，升得果兩三度，又點會有分別...分分鐘水裏面個溫差都超過呢個數...</blockquote><br />\n你都識講咁少鹽，點調味?<br />\n差幾度就係差幾度，你試下去高原，水只能去到九十度左右，啲麵一係生，一係熟到爛。</blockquote><br />\n你有冇煮過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係落少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係落粗鹽落到意粉夠味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗落好多都夠"},{"pid":"d25158786884cd145227ec63b4b814e54ebe1053","tid":455292,"uid":45431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:34:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自己試過，落左最大既分別係在於你其後有汁果陣啲味會融合啲</blockquote><br />\n我估係你嗰煮法有些許問題。<br />\n好多香港人煮完係就咁倒個汁上面撈，而事實上想好食同你所講既融和就要倒返落pan度炒下佢，等佢收返啲汁。"},{"pid":"54b50a90859e496a051886163e53642253eec3dd","tid":455292,"uid":43570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:34:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真係純粹調味....<br />\n<br />\n咁多水，咁少鹽，升得果兩三度，又點會有分別...分分鐘水裏面個溫差都超過呢個數...</blockquote><br />\n你都識講咁少鹽，點調味?<br />\n差幾度就係差幾度，你試下去高原，水只能去到九十度左右，啲麵一係生，一係熟到爛。</blockquote><br />\n因為人味覺好敏感....但物理現象唔係咁敏感...<br />\n<br />\n高原你應該係講煮即食面？即食面係設計過係某某溫度先有反應的，低溫trigger 唔到個化學反應當然唔熟，熟到爛係因為浸得太耐水。但過左個threshold 兩三度，只要唔trigger到下一個高溫反應就冇乜問題"},{"pid":"780aac066bbadd33fd2e71bba3c98bdffa243503","tid":455292,"uid":47095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:34:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇咁易痴住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個係油下話"},{"pid":"0ed68b8c8e96e0f5f16481aa34a76198ce0b4647","tid":455292,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:35:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真係純粹調味....<br />\n<br />\n咁多水，咁少鹽，升得果兩三度，又點會有分別...分分鐘水裏面個溫差都超過呢個數...</blockquote><br />\n你都識講咁少鹽，點調味?<br />\n差幾度就係差幾度，你試下去高原，水只能去到九十度左右，啲麵一係生，一係熟到爛。</blockquote><br />\n你有冇煮過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係落少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係落粗鹽落到意粉夠味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗落好多都夠</blockquote><br />\n講緊落兩匙鹽去兩litre水入邊煮麵，唔係最後上碟落鹽喎，大家係咪講緊唔同野?"},{"pid":"193d793141d5101a7030e17924e66800f30084b3","tid":455292,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:37:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真係純粹調味....<br />\n<br />\n咁多水，咁少鹽，升得果兩三度，又點會有分別...分分鐘水裏面個溫差都超過呢個數...</blockquote><br />\n你都識講咁少鹽，點調味?<br />\n差幾度就係差幾度，你試下去高原，水只能去到九十度左右，啲麵一係生，一係熟到爛。</blockquote><br />\n因為人味覺好敏感....但物理現象唔係咁敏感...<br />\n<br />\n高原你應該係講煮即食面？即食面係設計過係某某溫度先有反應的，低溫trigger 唔到個化學反應當然唔熟，熟到爛係因為浸得太耐水。但過左個threshold 兩三度，只要唔trigger到下一個高溫反應就冇乜問題</blockquote><br />\n唔係，係澱粉食品既本身品味，唔夠熱就要煮耐啲，煮耐左就會吸水爛。<br />\n調轉，夠熱就煮快啲，就會彈牙啲。"},{"pid":"684d03b215e8bc3cd22a415d113bcc107d14a3c6","tid":455292,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真係純粹調味....<br />\n<br />\n咁多水，咁少鹽，升得果兩三度，又點會有分別...分分鐘水裏面個溫差都超過呢個數...</blockquote><br />\n你都識講咁少鹽，點調味?<br />\n差幾度就係差幾度，你試下去高原，水只能去到九十度左右，啲麵一係生，一係熟到爛。</blockquote><br />\n因為人味覺好敏感....但物理現象唔係咁敏感...<br />\n<br />\n高原你應該係講煮即食面？即食面係設計過係某某溫度先有反應的，低溫trigger 唔到個化學反應當然唔熟，熟到爛係因為浸得太耐水。但過左個threshold 兩三度，只要唔trigger到下一個高溫反應就冇乜問題</blockquote><br />\n唔係，係澱粉食品既本身品味，唔夠熱就要煮耐啲，煮耐左就會吸水爛。<br />\n調轉，夠熱就煮快啲，就會彈牙啲。</blockquote><br />\n本身問題，我唔知自己點解打左品味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c2e0346302c75eaf5dd086903f0fea6e4a0a26","tid":455292,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:40:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真係純粹調味....<br />\n<br />\n咁多水，咁少鹽，升得果兩三度，又點會有分別...分分鐘水裏面個溫差都超過呢個數...</blockquote><br />\n你都識講咁少鹽，點調味?<br />\n差幾度就係差幾度，你試下去高原，水只能去到九十度左右，啲麵一係生，一係熟到爛。</blockquote><br />\n你有冇煮過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係落少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係落粗鹽落到意粉夠味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗落好多都夠</blockquote><br />\n講緊落兩匙鹽去兩litre水入邊煮麵，唔係最後上碟落鹽喎，大家係咪講緊唔同野?</blockquote><br />\n你可以自己試下有冇味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就咁落兩匙粗鹽落兩litre凍水 飲下睇下有冇味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602602562281604c5fe418aa69f90d008ae10791","tid":455292,"uid":43570,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:41:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真係純粹調味....<br />\n<br />\n咁多水，咁少鹽，升得果兩三度，又點會有分別...分分鐘水裏面個溫差都超過呢個數...</blockquote><br />\n你都識講咁少鹽，點調味?<br />\n差幾度就係差幾度，你試下去高原，水只能去到九十度左右，啲麵一係生，一係熟到爛。</blockquote><br />\n因為人味覺好敏感....但物理現象唔係咁敏感...<br />\n<br />\n高原你應該係講煮即食面？即食面係設計過係某某溫度先有反應的，低溫trigger 唔到個化學反應當然唔熟，熟到爛係因為浸得太耐水。但過左個threshold 兩三度，只要唔trigger到下一個高溫反應就冇乜問題</blockquote><br />\n唔係，係澱粉食品既本身品味，唔夠熱就要煮耐啲，煮耐左就會吸水爛。<br />\n調轉，夠熱就煮快啲，就會彈牙啲。</blockquote><br />\n冇錯，前題係溫度要夠，唔係一百度煮三分鐘嘅野，五十度煮六分鐘就得...<br />\n而且而家個問題係，水沸點上升三四度，對個煮食時間影響究竟有幾大？"},{"pid":"56c989070790818fefdd7e5f39363de1eaffac90","tid":455292,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:43:26.000Z","msg":"唔止落鹽，仲要落少少橄欖油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf6a0471ee3a6432e59f822e49091d318c2eb0a","tid":455292,"uid":77143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:43:37.000Z","msg":"唔好唸咁多，就係調味"},{"pid":"abdebd5c5df3078e7f907c5ec59f2030f0b99d42","tid":455292,"uid":73244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:50:07.000Z","msg":"令d水好飲d"},{"pid":"8823814c77875775c7a96d17a9e62d231fbb84fc","tid":455292,"uid":68732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:52:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有味d囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點解我唔落糖 ?</blockquote><br />\n屌你搞清楚鹽同糖既作用先上黎問啦<br />\n答你又唔撚信<br />\n唔係以為糖同鹽似樣就係同一類野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f9fbb57517cf1f2d317c3f24b1a27e00da515f","tid":455292,"uid":68732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:54:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有味d囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點解我唔落糖 ?</blockquote><br />\n屌你搞清楚鹽同糖既作用先上黎問啦<br />\n答你又唔撚信<br />\n唔係以為糖同鹽似樣就係同一類野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係唔信既自己上網查下咩叫鮮味<br />\n再查下咩叫鹽<br />\n<br />\n答你調味又唔撚信又串柒柒咁"},{"pid":"0f6cdccce00439e5339368c2fcfe659b7ee2abfb","tid":455292,"uid":17425,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:55:46.000Z","msg":"本身意大利人用海水煮，咁現代人好多用供水系統拎既淡水咪要加鹽囉"},{"pid":"6763da62ce401e62a6bb8830034141f74e36679a","tid":455292,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:57:26.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好落太多"},{"pid":"2a1e26c9583ea8b83489e29000030ec01e4ac2a2","tid":455292,"uid":53515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:58:12.000Z","msg":"不如你google下硬水同軟水點解先啦....."},{"pid":"97df09a8617a352634779fb1678ec57244d12410","tid":455292,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>沸點唔同左</blockquote><br />\n高左？</blockquote><br />\n低左<br />\n<br />\n另外，我估可能係<br />\n密度高左，令意粉味冇咁易流失<br />\n<br />\n加埋密度高左啲粉易浮啲，更易做到轉轉轉個效果<br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩吹，可能只係為左令啲粉有味</blockquote><br />\n沸點低左姐係, <br />\n姐係原本D水100度就滾<br />\n落左鹽, D水90度就滾<br />\n<br />\n會唔會係D意粉用低溫D, e.g. 90度, 去煮會好食D ?</blockquote><br />\n高左呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落左鹽可以上到10x度，水熱啲煮出黎好食啲</blockquote><br />\n但係水滾落意粉就熄火cum蓋浸意粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8840e4a850c54678894e13212a36f8df72572b7c","tid":455292,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:58:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身意大利人用海水煮，咁現代人好多用供水系統拎既淡水咪要加鹽囉</blockquote><br />\n痴線 鹹死"},{"pid":"25fe689ca2600ccfa22b5650eaaaf7c197897614","tid":455292,"uid":20835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:59:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身意大利人用海水煮，咁現代人好多用供水系統拎既淡水咪要加鹽囉</blockquote><br />\n一乾三濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601d37ad1e062123c6ba3ac22c328f41a8178d7c","tid":455292,"uid":45368,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:59:34.000Z","msg":"型d <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/115914_b8af7bb0b3a1dc91785569116dad9d07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F115914_b8af7bb0b3a1dc91785569116dad9d07.jpg&h=64030a05&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0b43dc7b3cac6805bb487b8832ddff016086462","tid":455292,"uid":53061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:00:39.000Z","msg":"因為外國人煮意粉果陣會係烚果陣調埋味"},{"pid":"4c519dba674d477092cfe21b818d0cd1583ed516","tid":455292,"uid":36663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:06:53.000Z","msg":"試過有一次唔記得落 啲意粉一咬落去幾乎完全冇味 嗰陣仲要係煮冇汁意粉齋用橄欖油大蒜細火炒 自此每次煮都記得一定要落鹽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d55308ecb283e2e793f3f1f3a2ff862df8a6be9","tid":455292,"uid":28031,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:12:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">減低滲透作用</span> <br />\n等條意粉煮完會彈牙啲</blockquote><br />\n大師, 呢話何解 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n基礎物理 <br />\n密度大既野（意粉）會傾向流向密度低（水）同時水又會滲翻入意粉<br />\n密度差越大 流得越多 即係意粉結構入面會多左水份 搞到條麵冇咁彈牙<br />\n<br />\n鹽水高密度過純水 所以滲入去既水份會少過用純水<br />\n所以煮完會彈牙啲"},{"pid":"6eb628e8b5ee38d923bf93b354ebb600d50864d4","tid":455292,"uid":1247,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:17:37.000Z","msg":"好多物理化學大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係廚藝領域上交流點解一樣食物要調味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n長知識了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca90592a885631c2e20924807aaab00d5bbd99a","tid":455292,"uid":52026,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:30:03.000Z","msg":"改變左水既磁通量<br />\n咁煮出黎既意粉口感 味道都會更好<br />\n利申：phd of food science"},{"pid":"77aa584cdf7e5bd0e37246fbba30b8d7f6dab670","tid":455292,"uid":15939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:31:41.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，出埋硬水軟水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n調味用架屌，你就咁用滾水都食得，不過要再落料加味囉"},{"pid":"b8dfedf9c05b8557141a1fbf9f4a3d4eeb7db881","tid":455292,"uid":14208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:34:07.000Z","msg":"弱智就唔好煮野食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01aaf899f0a90a10665ab1ec306c832b41d70f0b","tid":455292,"uid":144943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:36:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>型d <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/115914_b8af7bb0b3a1dc91785569116dad9d07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F115914_b8af7bb0b3a1dc91785569116dad9d07.jpg&h=64030a05&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做多咗"},{"pid":"696ec714e5505d8a866469f8aada7ea27ae3a0b5","tid":455292,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:52:47.000Z","msg":"味"},{"pid":"2114e75a6f1d066a429764d1324aba7e34c0cab1","tid":455292,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:56:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>沸點唔同左</blockquote><br />\n高左？</blockquote><br />\n低左<br />\n<br />\n另外，我估可能係<br />\n密度高左，令意粉味冇咁易流失<br />\n<br />\n加埋密度高左啲粉易浮啲，更易做到轉轉轉個效果<br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩吹，可能只係為左令啲粉有味</blockquote><br />\n沸點低左姐係, <br />\n姐係原本D水100度就滾<br />\n落左鹽, D水90度就滾<br />\n<br />\n會唔會係D意粉用低溫D, e.g. 90度, 去煮會好食D ?</blockquote><br />\n高左呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落左鹽可以上到10x度，水熱啲煮出黎好食啲</blockquote><br />\n但係水滾落意粉就熄火cum蓋浸意粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常size意粉要大火煮八分鐘，你真係浸得熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278ed88f193e456781001259fcff62fc1d871533","tid":455292,"uid":1533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:59:47.000Z","msg":"係落油"},{"pid":"2f60e9a364af71374ef36fcb3e24225c33db42d2","tid":455292,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:59:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真係純粹調味....<br />\n<br />\n咁多水，咁少鹽，升得果兩三度，又點會有分別...分分鐘水裏面個溫差都超過呢個數...</blockquote><br />\n你都識講咁少鹽，點調味?<br />\n差幾度就係差幾度，你試下去高原，水只能去到九十度左右，啲麵一係生，一係熟到爛。</blockquote><br />\n你有冇煮過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係落少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係落粗鹽落到意粉夠味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗落好多都夠</blockquote><br />\n講緊落兩匙鹽去兩litre水入邊煮麵，唔係最後上碟落鹽喎，大家係咪講緊唔同野?</blockquote><br />\n你可以自己試下有冇味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就咁落兩匙粗鹽落兩litre凍水 飲下睇下有冇味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你問我不如自己試下啦，兩茶匙鹽加兩litre水，真係幾乎試唔出。就咁飲都麻麻地感覺到，煮嗰七八分鐘可以對意粉有幾大影響?<br />\n利申: 試過無數次。"},{"pid":"6f92abf5d9a22f4c96f20f4a1cbe5c3afcee0f5f","tid":455292,"uid":22024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:04:57.000Z","msg":"咁都好拗<br />\n調吓味姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a113f27b262dd482202d73e68df1339c4fa185a","tid":455292,"uid":27359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:29:37.000Z","msg":"比啲底味囉"},{"pid":"1160a77600d3807e81c18c2b04e0f0a61f2437fc","tid":455292,"uid":27359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真係純粹調味....<br />\n<br />\n咁多水，咁少鹽，升得果兩三度，又點會有分別...分分鐘水裏面個溫差都超過呢個數...</blockquote><br />\n你都識講咁少鹽，點調味?<br />\n差幾度就係差幾度，你試下去高原，水只能去到九十度左右，啲麵一係生，一係熟到爛。</blockquote><br />\n你有冇煮過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係落少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係落粗鹽落到意粉夠味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗落好多都夠</blockquote><br />\n講緊落兩匙鹽去兩litre水入邊煮麵，唔係最後上碟落鹽喎，大家係咪講緊唔同野?</blockquote><br />\n你可以自己試下有冇味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就咁落兩匙粗鹽落兩litre凍水 飲下睇下有冇味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你問我不如自己試下啦，兩茶匙鹽加兩litre水，真係幾乎試唔出。就咁飲都麻麻地感覺到，煮嗰七八分鐘可以對意粉有幾大影響?<br />\n利申: 試過無數次。</blockquote><br />\n落兩茶匙唔怪得無味<br />\n啲意粉水係要鹹到去taste like sea water"},{"pid":"ad14502153e96ba86573a04f338eef4ab1e20587","tid":455292,"uid":27359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:31:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係落油</blockquote><br />\n坐左幾耐監呀 仲落油"},{"pid":"db9405815ba913138da9267c4444f6685ea04e29","tid":455292,"uid":129054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:33:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00df0b0ab8a9aa8634ad486966b693dc40dde7f1","tid":455292,"uid":5007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:35:00.000Z","msg":"al dente"},{"pid":"de06a7d6305c6e7c331c4197c981344f4888fbc1","tid":455292,"uid":27359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:36:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>沸點唔同左</blockquote><br />\n高左？</blockquote><br />\n低左<br />\n<br />\n另外，我估可能係<br />\n密度高左，令意粉味冇咁易流失<br />\n<br />\n加埋密度高左啲粉易浮啲，更易做到轉轉轉個效果<br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩吹，可能只係為左令啲粉有味</blockquote><br />\n中學有無讀science呀 <br />\n會高左呀戇鳩<br />\n同埋1kg水要加30g鹽先升到0.5度沸點<br />\n你落撚到咁多呀？"},{"pid":"eb0515daefa59a41c3a93e6f8a178c46ea1e85f0","tid":455292,"uid":129054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:36:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c08b0b25fd6bbde81065415f4d12b29738fe6def","tid":4